<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٤٣٧⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>٣٩٩٢ -<span class="c5"> عَنْ دَاوُدَ بْنِ إِبْرَاهِيمَ قَالَ:</span> سَأَلْتُ طَاوُسًا،<span class="c5"> قُلْتُ:</span> أَرْكَعُ رَكْعَتَيْنِ وَالْمُؤَذِّنُ يُقِيمُ؟<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«أَوَ تُطِيقُ ذَلِكَ؟»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>